data.description: Discover exceptional value in the sought-after Waldrop Hills neighborhood with this spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home, ideally located near top-rated schools and shopping conveniences. The welcoming entrance leads to an elegant formal living room and a separate dining room, perfect for hosting. An eat-in kitchen, featuring views of the large living area, ensures the cook is never out of the conversation. Upstairs, the primary suite impresses with vaulted ceilings and a sizable ensuite, alongside two additional bedrooms and a versatile bonus room that can serve as a fourth bedroom. Recent updates include new LVP flooring upstairs, adding modern elegance. A fenced backyard offers a private outdoor retreat for relaxation or entertainment.
